Package: comtrade
Title: Access and Analyse UN Comtrade International Trade Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Charles", "Coverdale", , "charlesfcoverdale@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Download and analyse international merchandise and services trade
    data from the United Nations Comtrade database
    <https://comtradeplus.un.org/>. Retrieve bilateral trade flows, compute
    trade analytics (revealed comparative advantage, trade concentration,
    trade balance), and convert between commodity classifications (HS, SITC,
    BEC). Covers 200+ reporter countries, 60+ years of goods trade data
    (1962-present), and services trade via EBOPS. Requires a free API key
    from <https://comtradedeveloper.un.org/>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-GB
URL: https://github.com/charlescoverdale/comtrade
BugReports: https://github.com/charlescoverdale/comtrade/issues
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
